713
00:31:51,420 --> 00:31:52,700
Ancheng, listen to me.

714
00:31:52,700 --> 00:31:54,860
Most of my projects
are handled properly.

715
00:31:55,140 --> 00:31:56,820
It's just that I can't

716
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,380
