717
00:31:59,420 --> 00:32:00,340
Like

718
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,540
the Fang family.

719
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:03,380
You understand, right?

720
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:04,300
I don't.

721
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,300
I don't know how Dad would react.

722
00:32:06,580 --> 00:32:07,620
No, no, no.

723
00:32:07,780 --> 00:32:09,500
