736
00:32:42,820 --> 00:32:44,180
I won't tell Chairman for now.

737
00:32:44,740 --> 00:32:46,020
You've worked with him for many years.

738
00:32:46,740 --> 00:32:47,660
But,

739
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:49,540
you must return

