785
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:44,220
I honestly thought...

786
00:34:45,820 --> 00:34:46,660
You scared me.

787
00:34:46,660 --> 00:34:47,580
It's fine.

788
00:35:01,540 --> 00:35:02,900
Good thing you didn't accept it.

789
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:04,500
Otherwise,

790
00:35:04,940 --> 00:35:06,180
