798
00:35:29,460 --> 00:35:31,060
We have to face this together.

799
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:31,980
Don't handle it on your own.

800
00:35:31,980 --> 00:35:32,900
Anlan.

801
00:35:33,220 --> 00:35:34,140
Keep your voice down.

802
00:35:34,940 --> 00:35:36,380
