803
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:42,380
How are you?

804
00:35:42,380 --> 00:35:43,300
Are you okay?

805
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:44,580
I don't have any wounds.

806
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:46,900
It's just that I feel like

807
00:35:47,180 --> 00:35:48,500
