809
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:53,660
this feeling for the rest of my life.

810
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:55,580
It's like you know

811
00:35:55,580 --> 00:35:56,660
what will happen,

812
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:58,460
you just can't control it.

813
00:36:00,100 --> 00:36:01,060
For the first time, I felt

814
00:36:02,180 --> 00:36:03,140
life's ending

815
00:36:03,140 --> 00:36:04,420
