828
00:36:28,500 --> 00:36:29,570
- Anlan.
- Hey, stop.

829
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:32,700
Just focus on running more.

830
00:36:32,700 --> 00:36:33,820
You can run faster than they do.

831
00:36:33,820 --> 00:36:34,700
Then you'll be safe.

832
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:35,620
Jiang Anlan.

833
00:36:36,060 --> 00:36:37,180
If you ever get into trouble,

834
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:38,100
