839
00:36:47,260 --> 00:36:48,180
No problem.

840
00:36:49,220 --> 00:36:51,300
Ancheng, you really need to be careful.

841
00:36:51,300 --> 00:36:52,580
You're my only brother,

842
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:55,700
