853
00:37:27,180 --> 00:37:28,100
So, what should I do?

854
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,780
I've been wondering what I'd do myself.

855
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,780
Would I waver?

856
00:37:35,660 --> 00:37:36,540
But I realized deep down,

857
00:37:36,540 --> 00:37:37,900
